OL,3,CSister of woman murdered by family
OL,4,Ccalls for legal definition of honour
OL,5,Cabuse
OL,7,FThe sister of a woman who was murdered
OL,8,Fby her father, uncle and cousins is
OL,9,Fcalling for honour-based violence to
OL,10,Fbe given a legal definition.
OL,12,FBanaz Mahmod was killed by male
OL,13,Fmembers of her family in London in
OL,14,F2006 after she left an abusive,
OL,15,Farranged marriage and began a
OL,16,Frelationship with another man.
OL,18,FShe was forced into the marriage when
OL,19,Fshe was just 17. After two years, she
OL,20,Freported her husband to the police and
OL,21,Fmoved back home.
