OL,7,FNot long afterwards, she was murdered
OL,8,F- her body put into a suitcase and
OL,9,Fburied in a garden Handsworth,
OL,10,FBirmingham.
OL,12,FHer father, uncle and two cousins were
OL,13,Ffound guilty of her killing and jailed.
OL,15,FNow, her sister Payzee Mahmod is
OL,16,Fjoining calls for a legal definition
OL,17,Fof honour-based abuse, so the crimes
OL,18,Fcan be recorded accurately and
OL,19,Fauthorities get a true picture of the
OL,20,Fscale of the problem.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/11
