OL,7,FSpeaking at a conference in
OL,8,FLoughborough to discuss honour-based
OL,9,Fabuse, Payzee said she was also forced
OL,10,Finto an arranged marriage. She was
OL,11,Fonly 16 and her husband was 30.
OL,13,FHe stopped her from going to college,
OL,14,Fforced her to cook and clean, and
OL,15,Fafter she left him, threatened her
OL,16,Fwith the same fate as her sister.
OL,18,FPayzee is now a campaigner at the
OL,19,FIranian & Kurdish Women's Rights
OL,20,FOrganisation.
