OL,7,F"We know that this is happening all
OL,8,Fover the country in many communities.
OL,9,FWe know that honour-based abuse runs
OL,10,Fthrough pretty much every community."
OL,12,FShe added that in "a lot of the
OL,13,Fcommunities that are affected, these
OL,14,Fconversations have a wall of silence
OL,15,Fin front of them, and people treat
OL,16,Fthese topics as taboo.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/11
