OL,7,F"We are seeing forced marriage, we are
OL,8,Fseeing honour-based violence, we are
OL,9,Fseeing female genital mutilation, so
OL,10,Flet's talk about it. Let's talk about
OL,11,Fwhy it's happening and how we can stop
OL,12,Fit from happening. It's all about
OL,13,Feducation and also empowerment.
OL,15,F'Men are a huge part of the solution'
OL,17,F"We need to be talking to young boys
OL,18,Fin school, we need to make sure that
OL,19,Ffamilies are equipped with the
OL,20,Fresources to have those conversations
OL,21,Fat home.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/11
