OL,7,F"There are men who are victims of
OL,8,Fhonour-based abuse. They are forced
OL,9,Finto a position of power to uphold the
OL,10,Ffamily's honour and reputation.
OL,12,F"Although they're part of the problem,
OL,13,Fa huge part of it, men are also a huge
OL,14,Fpart of the solution."
OL,16,F'Honour-based abuse hasn't gone
OL,17,Fanywhere'
