OL,7,FSukhi Kaur, the chair of the Board of
OL,8,FTrustees at Sikh Women's Aid, said:
OL,9,F"Honour-based abuse hasn't gone
OL,10,Fanywhere.
OL,12,F"Migrant communities, local
OL,13,Fcommunities, we've been here for over
OL,14,F50, 60, 70 years, but this issue we
OL,15,Fhaven't got it statutorily defined.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/11
