OL,5,Cabuse
OL,7,F"The conversations around honour-based
OL,8,Fabuse are very silo-ed. So it's really
OL,9,Fabout getting everyone talking about
OL,10,Fwhat honour-based abuse is, how do we
OL,11,Fspot it and most importantly, how to
OL,12,Fsave women's lives because that's what
OL,13,Fwe're all in the business of doing."
OL,15,F"Domestic abuse nationally is on the
OL,16,Fincrease, so if domestic abuse is
OL,17,Fincreasing, honour-based abuse is
OL,18,Fdefinitely increasing.
OL,20,F'This is not just a crime that affects
OL,21,Fa certain or particular community'
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/11
