OL,7,F"We have ever-changing populations
OL,8,Facross the United Kingdom now. The
OL,9,Fface and shape of honour-based abuse
OL,10,Fare definitely changing.
OL,12,F"With the increase of technology, tech
OL,13,Fabuse, it's now easy to track and
OL,14,Fsurveil. We find these crimes are
OL,15,Flooked at in isolation, and they're
OL,16,Fnot looked at as a wider pattern of
OL,17,Fhonour-based abuse.
