OL,7,FSukhi Kaur said honour-based abuse is
OL,8,Fnot just an Asian problem, and has
OL,9,Fseen examples of it in Christian
OL,10,Fcommunities and with Jehovah's
OL,11,FWitnesses.
OL,13,FShe added: "This is widespread because
OL,14,Fit's about attitudes and beliefs...
OL,15,Fthis is not just a crime that affects
OL,16,Fa certain or particular community, it
OL,17,Fis spread across multiple faith-based
OL,18,Fcommunities.
OL,20,FITV News Central has approached the
OL,21,FHome Office for a response.
